snippet.title: Cat in the Box - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Cat in the Box is a horror adventure game. Help the poor girl explore the mansion and escape from unknown entities that are pursuing her.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1257410/Cat_in_the_Box/

Cat in the Box © 2020 Gustav. Soundtrack produced by Majesty & Gustav. Published by PsychoFlux Entertainment. All rights reserved.
